## Delivery Semantics

This design commits to {{deliverySemantics}} delivery. Exactly-once
delivery is deliberately not claimed — no broker provides it end to end —
so the consumer side carries the burden:

- At-least-once: duplicates are possible; every consumer effect must be idempotent (see Idempotency).
- At-most-once: loss is possible; state the business justification for tolerating dropped events.
